data.eml:eml: A new genus and species of congrid eel from the Philippines (Anguillliformes: Congridae: Bathymyrinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Smith, David G. (2018): A new genus and species of congrid eel from the Philippines (Anguillliformes: Congridae: Bathymyrinae). Zootaxa 4454 (1): 78-83, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4454.1.9
